Personal No Wahala Loan

The Personal No Wahala Loan facility is a mass market product that offers credit facilities to salaried to enable them meet personal financing needs.

Features

  • Tenor: Up to 24 months
  • Maximum amount: Ghc 5,000

Eligibility

  • Employees at lower end of retail market

Benefits

  • Ability to finance emergency needs without much hassle
  • No collateral required
